feedPosts.description: Yesterday we planted 50 trees in our local park. The community came together and it was incredible to see everyone working together for a greener future.
feedPosts.challenge: Join us next month for another tree planting event!

feedPosts.title: Teaching Tech Skills to Seniors
feedPosts.description: Spent the afternoon teaching basic computer skills to my elderly neighbors. Their enthusiasm for learning was inspiring!
feedPosts.challenge: Help someone learn something new this week

feedPosts.title: Hackathon Results - 15 New Apps for Nonprofits
feedPosts.description: Our weekend hackathon was a huge success! We developed 15 new applications to help local nonprofits with their digital needs.
feedPosts.challenge: Help us implement these solutions in your community

feedPosts.title: Tree Planting Initiative - 100 Trees Planted
feedPosts.description: Our community planted 100 trees this weekend! Each tree will help combat climate change and provide habitat for local wildlife.
feedPosts.challenge: Plant a tree in your neighborhood

feedPosts.title: Amazing Beach Cleanup Success!
feedPosts.description: Yesterday we collected over 500kg of waste from our local beach. The community came together and it was incredible to see everyone working for a cleaner environment.
feedPosts.challenge: Join us next month for another cleanup event!

feedPosts.title: Digital Literacy Program Launch
feedPosts.description: We're excited to launch our digital literacy program for seniors. Teaching basic computer skills to help them stay connected.
feedPosts.challenge: Help someone learn something new this week

feedPosts.description: Our community health workshop reached 25 people today. We covered stress management, mindfulness, and building healthy habits.

feedPosts.title: Beach Cleanup Success - 500kg of waste collected!
feedPosts.description: Our amazing volunteers spent the weekend cleaning up the local beach. We collected over 500kg of plastic waste and marine debris. This is what community action looks like!
feedPosts.challenge: Marine pollution is threatening our oceans. Every piece of plastic we remove makes a difference.

feedPosts.title: Hackathon Results - 15 new apps for nonprofits
feedPosts.description: Our 48-hour hackathon brought together 50 developers who created 15 innovative apps for local nonprofits. Technology for social good!
feedPosts.challenge: Nonprofits often lack the resources for custom software solutions. We're bridging that gap.

feedPosts.title: Community Mural Project - Final Reveal
feedPosts.description: After 3 months of work, our community mural is complete! 50 artists, 200 volunteers, one beautiful story.
feedPosts.challenge: Public spaces often lack cultural representation. We're bringing community stories to life through art.

feedPosts.title: Mental Health Awareness Workshop - Success
feedPosts.description: Over 200 people attended our mental health workshop. Breaking the stigma, one conversation at a time.
feedPosts.challenge: Mental health stigma prevents people from seeking help. We're creating safe spaces for open dialogue.

feedPosts.title: Community Garden Harvest - 500lbs of vegetables
feedPosts.description: Our community garden produced 500lbs of fresh vegetables this season! Food security starts in our neighborhoods.
feedPosts.challenge: Food deserts leave communities without access to fresh produce. We're growing food where people live.
